data.description: Welcome to this Absolutely STUNNING home situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in Oakhurst!!  This home features 4/5 bedrooms with 3.5 bathrooms, formal dining, study, and open concept living/kitchen.  From the moment you walk in you are welcomed with that warmth of "I AM HOME" felling with the high ceilings, beautiful wrought iron staircase, and the open concept floor plan showcasing the chef style kitchen with granite countertops!  The spacious Primary room features a spa like En Suite with a large walk in closet and the upstairs has 3 generous bedrooms and a flex room that could be another bedroom, media room, or exercise/craft room.  Have a nice cup of coffee on the covered back patio and enjoy the yard where there are endless possibilities since there is plenty of room for a pool and/or a Texas Size BBQ!  Don't miss out on this home in this Golf Course Community that offers lots of amenities!  Close to shopping, dining, and major freeways to make it easy access around town!
